item.title: GDAL on Travis
item.description: GDAL on Travis ðŸ”— This article is meant to be a relative process guide on issues around installing GDAL on Travis CI. Frustrations around finding helpful articles have led to this writing. The steps follow an error reproduction to a solid solution for the issue. The GDAL version installed on the chosen machine must match the package library version installed into your project. Example, glad-config -v == pip freeze | grep GDAL.
